extends layout

block content
  .container(style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; text-align: center; padding: 20px;")
    
    h1(style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px;")
      | Blockchain Visual Demo

    p(style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 30px; max-width: 800px; line-height: 1.6;")
      | This is a visual demonstration of how Blockchain technology works. 
      | You will see various actions such as hash generation, block mining, Blockchain creation, 
      | and how difficulty levels affect nonce calculations.
 
    // Example of Dynamic Content Section (Additional Details)
    .block-info(style="margin-top: 50px; background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); width: 100%; max-width: 900px;")
      h2(style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px;")
        | Blockchain Demo Details
      p(style="font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.6;")
        | Here's where you will visually see how different processes like hash generation, mining, and Blockchain structure creation unfold in real-time.
        

    // Footer Section (for additional links, credits, etc.)
    footer(style="margin-top: 60px; font-size: 1rem; color: #888;")
      p
        | Created with ❤️ by Blockchain  
